## Erlang VM arguments for AeroVision on Nerves

## Node name (not distributed — single node embedded device)
-sname aerovision

## Cookie for distributed Erlang (not used, but required by OTP)
-setcookie aerovision_cookie

## Use the interactive shell via IEx on the console UART
-noshell
-user elixir
-run elixir start_cli
-extra --no-halt
